title: Capitol
description: Serves meat, veg options available. Has tofu dishes (spicy or regular), and rice is extra charge. Inexpensive, compared to other sit-down restaurants in Venice. Located in Campo Santi Filippo e Giacomo, going from Piazza San Marco, over Ponte Della Canonica (bridge), then just down on your right as you walk into St Marks Square.
streetAddress: 4294, Campo SS. Filippo e Giacomo, Venizia
